CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 8, 1959, pg. B9 reads: "Frog Week Events Highlight Gay Social Season - Surrounded - George Pitts is surrounded by smiling lovelies at the Frogs' formal in Gateway Plaza last week. Top are Mrs. Jane Moore and Mrs. Elva Busey.  Mrs. Phyllis Pitts is at bottom row left with Mrs. William G. Nunn Jr. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: George Pitts standing between Jane Moore and Elva Busey, with Phyllis Pitts and Frances Bell Nunn seated at table, in Gateway Plaza for FROGS formal
